{"tid":1576354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實可以正式宣布香港進入緊急狀態","createTime":"2019-09-17T08:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T14:46:53.000Z","uid":120070,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7361b7745213facbda3b69ae487998000c3058b3","tid":1576354,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:07:22.000Z","msg":"呢家每日都不停有人被自殺 墜海墜樓⋯<br />\n滅聲噤聲  太子過成個禮拜先剪幾幅圖比你 假撚到<br />\n到今日都唔公開 驚死人知<br />\n<br />\n新屋嶺一樣身有屎 太平紳士都首次 唔入得去探監<br />\n<br />\n香港人權已經去到近乎 0 <br />\n咁都未係緊急狀態 <br />\n<br />\n究竟要點樣先係港豬的末日？ 一齊討論下<br />\n<br />\n呢家啲同伴 一隻一隻比人車出去<br />\n港豬繼續係農場打工 被餵飼<br />\n毫無反抗能力 ，有一班比較衝既都比人捉去劏<br />\n究竟港豬幾時先醒覺？<br />\n<br />\n滅聲禁聲殺人滅口 個套已經提早黎到香港<br />\n呢家送唔撚送中 已經唔撚係最重點了 大家覺唔覺得？<br />\n<br />\n人權平等自由之戰 既戰火已經提早點起<br />\nIf you need war, they give us a war<br />\nDont u feel?<br />\n<br />\n到底港豬仲可以點反抗<br />\n等馬騮黎幫 衝開農場閘口？"},{"pid":"120f77bfa12a2a0a899c442444e17c951868848d","tid":1576354,"uid":76609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:07:54.000Z","msg":"由我地自己宣佈"},{"pid":"a627846c313ee106761af345167ca50255e8fae8","tid":1576354,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:09:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8f35133af91b591fd1dc0e443e171433a2c777","tid":1576354,"uid":265179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"120f77bfa12a2a0a899c442444e17c951868848d","tid":1576354,"uid":76609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:07:54.000Z","msg":"由我地自己宣佈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:09:34.000Z","msg":"yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1e0e51d0176a28eec39238b4926204ca31d979","tid":1576354,"uid":120070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite